    "summary": {
      "title": "Summary",
      "columns": 1,
      "hidden": false,
      "content": "<p><strong>Python</strong> Backend with <strong>+15</strong> years building production systems: <strong>REST APIs</strong> with <strong>FastAPI</strong> and <strong>Django</strong>, complex integrations (<strong>REST, XMLRPC, SOA</strong>), <strong>Automation</strong>, <strong>Microservices</strong> and legacy system migration. Specialist in <strong>Odoo ERP</strong>, electronic invoicing, and <strong>ETL</strong> processes on <strong>PostgreSQL</strong>. I manage my own infrastructure (<strong>Proxmox, Docker, Kubernetes, CI/CD</strong>) where I develop, test and deploy end-to-end solutions. Experience across multiple sectors: finance, retail, manufacturing, telecommunications and services. I complement my backend profile with hands-on <strong>AI Engineering</strong> experience: designing <strong>RAG Pipelines</strong>, <strong>Agentic AI</strong>, <strong>Prompt Engineering</strong> workflows and solutions with <strong>LLM</strong>, applying AI to solve real business problems.</p>"
    },
